' description: hand_off_session baton 接力 sequence — 4 主路径 (cwd 反查 / 双模式分流 / spawn + adopt + task / cleanup)
' last_updated: 2026-05-29
@startuml hand-off-session-flow

title hand_off_session — baton 接力 sequence (4 主路径)

actor Caller as C
participant "hand_off facade" as H
participant "plan resolve\n(plan-driven 才用)" as I
participant "spawn 控制器" as SP
participant "数据表\n(会话 / 团队 / 任务)" as DB
participant "baton 收尾\n(关 teammate + 归档 caller)" as BC
participant "会话管理器 + SDK" as SM

== 入口: 白名单 + cwd 反查 ==

C -> H: invoke(plan_id?, prompt?, cwd?, adapter?, team_name?,\n  adopt_teammates?, archive_caller?, team_task_policy?, ...)
H -> DB: 反查 caller cwd / cwdReleaseMarker
note right of H
  入口拦截器: 白名单 deny external (起 SDK 子进程 fork bomb 风险)
  DB throw / row null → fail-open 退化 + console.warn
end note

== 段 1: 双模式分流 ==

alt plan-driven (plan_id 传)
  H -> I: 解析 plan
  I -> I: 按 fallback 链找 plan 文件 + 校验 + 构造 cold start prompt
  I --> H: { planFilePath, worktreePath, mainRepo, coldStartPrompt, isExternalWorktree }
  H -> H: cwd 默认 = mainRepo (cwd resilience)
  note right of H
    external worktree (worktree 不在 mainRepo 子树) →
    handler 自动把 mainRepo 加进 spawn args.extra_allow_write
    (claude-code workspace-write 沙盒额外 writable roots,
     让新 SDK session 能写 plan 文件)
  end note
else generic (无 plan_id)
  H -> H: 直接组装 generic 上下文 (cold start prompt = args.prompt 或默认)
  H -> H: cwd 默认 = caller cwd (与 plan-driven 不同)
end

H -> H: cwd 兜底链 + 失效自动回退

== 段 2: adopt 预检 + prompt 装配 + spawn + task 三态 ==

opt adopt_teammates=true (spawn 前必先做 N5 fail-fast + 装 adopt block)
  H -> DB: ≥1 lead 硬约束: caller 至少在 1 个 team 是 lead
  note right of DB
    无 active lead membership → spawn 之前直接 reject
    (不 spawn / 不 archive caller, fail-fast 不变量)
  end note
  H -> DB: 收集 archived team / archived teammate filter (排除 ghost)
  H -> H: 装 adopt context block → 注入 coldStartPromptForSDK
end

H -> SP: spawn (handOffMode=true → 跳防御 + 不写 spawn-link)
SP -> SM: 起 SDK 子进程 (prompt 已含 adopt block 如有)
SP --> H: { newSid, teamId?, spawnPromptMessageId? }

opt adopt_teammates=true (spawn 后)
  H -> DB: swapLead 转交 lead 角色 (per team loop, firstTeam 优先)
  note right of DB
    firstTeam swap 失败 → 回滚 newSid + reject
    非 firstTeam 失败 → 软失败继续 (failed.reason 透传)
  end note
end

opt archive_caller=true (默认)
  H -> DB: 按 team_task_policy 三态过继 task\n(clear-team / preserve-team / skip)
  note right of DB
    reassign throw 仅 warn 不阻塞
    preserve-team + newSid 未 adopt 该 team → policyWarning=\n  'preserve-team-unadopted-teams' + unadoptedTeamIds 透传
  end note
end

== 段 3: baton cleanup (与 archive_plan 共享 helper) ==

H -> BC: runBatonCleanup({callerSid, adoptTeammates, archiveCaller})
opt adopt_teammates=false AND archive_caller=true AND caller 是 lead
  BC -> SM: phase 1: 关 caller 同 team 全部 teammate\n(excludeSessionIds={newSid} 防 spawn 加入的 newSid 被一并关)
end
note right of BC
  phase 1 跳过条件 (6 状态完整 enum, baton-cleanup.ts:166-174):
  - **null** (成功路径含 closed=[] 的 caller=lead 但 team 内无其他 active teammate)
  - **'adopt-keep-implicit'** (adopt_teammates=true → teammate 已转给 newSid; Phase 4 引入)
  - **'archive-caller-false-keep'** (archive_caller=false → caller 保活; CHANGELOG_169 F4)
  - **'caller-not-lead'** (caller 不是 lead 含 external sentinel)
  - **'all-lead-teams-archived'** (caller 是 lead 但所有 team 已 archived; REVIEW_56 §F6 R2)
  - **'phase-1-error'** (phase 1 内部 throw 兜底; REVIEW_56 §F6 codex MED-3)
end note
opt archive_caller=true (默认)
  BC -> SM: phase 2: 归档 caller session
  note right of SM
    archive throw → archived='failed' warn-only
  end note
end
BC --> H: { teammatesShutdown, archived }

== 段 4: 收口 ok return ==

H --> C: ok({ mode, sessionId, cwd, teamId?, archived, teammatesShutdown,\n  adopted? (preserved/failed/teamsTotal), taskReassignment (status/count/policy) })

@enduml
